Package: bib2acad
Type: Package
Title: Convert Bibtex to Markdown for the Hugo Academic Theme
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peter", "Baumgartner", email = "petzi53@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Lorenzo", "Busetto", email = "lbusett@gmail.com", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Convert records of a BibTeX file (.bib) to separate .md files
    for the publications folder of the Hugo Academic Theme. Store optionally
    each record with the same name as a separate .bib file. 
